parameters: Flora: "So, are you ready? Let's go, Liese."

As Flora chants a spell, both of their bodies begin to shine and they
start to transfer to another world.

Flora: "Spatial coordinates set... Target, the floating world
\N[261]\N[262]!"

Flora: "This is the world I live in, \N[261]. Unlike your world,
Liese, the continent I grew up on floats in the sky."
Liese: "Wow, that's amazing... It really feels like an adventure."

Flora: "Liese, as a Warrior of Light, you must save this world from a
calamity known as the Void."

Flora: "\N[261] is the central hub that connects different worlds. If
it's swallowed by the Void, other worlds will disappear too."
Flora: "I will support you as \N[13], so let's work hard together."
Flora: "And now, we are here in the eastern part..."

Flora: "Our goal was \N[262], but... it looks like our transfer
location was significantly off. Probably due to a curse cast by
monsters."

Flora: "First, we need to get through this forest and head for \N[264]
located here."
Use the \N[261] world map to move to different locations.

By talking with townspeople and clearing specific events, you'll
unlock more places to travel to.
※地下道を見つけたら非表示にする

If you cross \N[264] and reach the coast, you can see an island...
It's not too far away, but it's definitely impossible to swim across.
Flora: "That's the island, right... Hmm, what should we do?"

After walking along the coastline for a while, I arrived at a rocky
area.
Liese: "Hey, what is that over there...?"
Flora: "That looks like... an entrance underground? Maybe a tunnel?!"
Found an underground passage on the rocky coast!
